    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained rice</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low until very gently bubbling and cook, covered, for 15 min</p><p>Once the rice has had 15 min, remove the pot from the heat and keep covered</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
