            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, combine your<strong> tomato</strong> <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in a bowl with 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> soy ketchup</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
