        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once melted, drain then add your <strong>king prawns</strong>,<strong> sliced garlic </strong>and<strong> shichimi togarashi </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through – these are your <strong>garlic & shichimi togarashi king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1681807099761-x200.jpg",
