            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked through, transfer the <strong>garlic & shichimi togarashi king prawns </strong>(reserve the pan!) to the pot with the rice</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>blanched peas </strong>and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cover and set aside – this is your <strong>king prawn rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
