            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, pour<strong> </strong>enough of the<strong> omelette mix </strong>into the pan in a rough circle to make 1 <strong>omelette blanket</strong> per person</p><p>Cook for 20 secs or until the omelette mix is cooked all the way through, then transfer to a small plate – this is your <strong>omelette blanket</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
