            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Press the <strong>king prawn rice </strong>into a bowl and turn out</p><p>Top with an <strong>omelette blanket</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>soy ketchup</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>crispy onions </strong>– this is your<strong> Japanese-style omurice with garlic & shichimi togarashi king prawns</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
